Text.Value: All services suspended until the current threat in Ramazith's Tower is neutralised. Have a magical day!
'Projection'.
Retraction acknowledged.
*Lorroakan's illusion is blissfully unaware of its caster's demise, but remains bound to its duties.*
'Trade'.
How else can I help you today?
False. Please do not attempt to lie to Master Lorroakan's projection.

EditorData.NodeContext: Could be funny to do 'Master Lorroakan' and then '-'s projection' almost as an aisde

Text.Value: Welcome, dear patron, to Sorcerous Sundries.

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Gwen Lee] HUM_M_Rig_DFLT_CINE_Bows_ArmsOut_01 seems to be a nice greeting for him.

Text.Value: Enjoy our unmatched selection!
Feast your eyes!
You're sure to find what you're looking for.
What will it be?
Your request has been previously denied due to INSUFFICIENT INTIMIDATION.
To browse our wares, say 'TRADE'. To provide information about the Nightsong, say 'NIGHTSONG'.
Please come again soon!
Your request has been previously denied due to INCORRECT FACE.
To learn more about the search for the Nightsong, say 'NIGHTSONG'. To learn more about Master Lorroakan, say 'LORROAKAN'. To learn more about my good self, say 'PROJECTION'.
Because Master Lorroakan is engaged in important work, I take care of such banalities as speaking with customers.
'Taxes'.
Don't you recognise Marvin Hudd when you see him?
Tax money has already been donated for the purpose of this projection's self-preservation.
No.
Threat detected. Commence amelioration protocol.

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Projection hands off cash below screen.

Text.Value: I am an un-person in service of the revered wizard Lorroakan, proprietor of this fine establishment.
Thank you! Please come again soon, and have a magical day!
The Nightsong is a relic hidden in an underground temple beneath a settlement near the river Chionthar.
Hold on - you said you're an un-person? What's that?
To truly know Master Lorroakan is the work of a lifetime. Suffice it to say he is a powerful, important man whose powers exceed the limitations by which most wizards are constrained.
Forgive this error in my analysis. Hello Mister Marvin Hudd. Please find your payment in full.

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Projection hands off cash below screen.

Text.Value: Tax money has already been allotted for your personal use.
'Lorroakan'.
Yes.
Looks like I have the wrong building. My apologies.
You are not Mister Marvin Hudd, the collections officer assigned to this establishment.
He resides in Ramazith's Tower. Anyone bearing information leading to the capture of the Nightsong may gain an audience with him.
The great and powerful Lorroakan, offering our humble group an audience? We are honoured.

EditorData.NodeContext: Dripping with sarcasm - Gale doesn't think much of Lorroakan

Text.Value: Fork over what you owe, or I'll crush your head.
Line of inquiry terminated. How else might I be of assistance?
Trust me, your taxes will be put to better use in my hands.
Welcome back to Sorcerous Sundries! How can I help you?

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Gwen Lee] HUM_M_Rig_DFLT_CINE_Bows_ArmsOut_01 seems to be a nice greeting for him.

Text.Value: 'Nightsong'.
I'm sorry. I didn't understand your query.
I've changed my mind.
If you are a city official here to collect dues, say 'TAXES'. For all other inquiries, say 'OTHER'.
'Other'.
Master Lorroakan is offering a considerable sum for the object's retrieval.
Please proceed upstairs for further instructions.
I've heard enough.
Logic detected; petition approved. Enjoy!

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Projection hands off cash below screen.

Text.Value: Leave.
It has come to my attention that there is a BITTER ADVENTURER located OUTSIDE the shop! Not to worry. We will quickly handle this disturbance for your comfort and safety.

EditorData.NodeContext: Like an answering machine for a chain business or automated customer service bot where the words in all caps were added into the sentence separately

Text.Value: This establishment's dues have been paid in full. See you soon, Mister Marvin Hudd.
Threat detected. Commence silent treatment.
The provision of information that leads to the retrieval of the Nightsong is worth a great deal to Master Lorroakan. Do you have information regarding the Nightsong?
Your request has been previously denied due to POOR REASONING.
Fallacy detected. Petition denied.
I am the product of an ingenious bit of magic performed by Master Lorroakan. I am blessed with sufficient intelligence to adequately run and protect this shop, Sorcerous Sundries.
Until next we meet! Is there anything else I can help you with?
'Nightsong'.

Synopsis: Projection dialog acting as Sorcerous Sundries' clerk in case of Rolan's death. They are basically the  an automated calling system with prerecorded messages. He also has the ability to cast a portal to take players to the real Lorroakan.
